<div class="container">
<h1>Sign Petition</h1>
<div class="description">
    
 <img class="plane" src="/on_plane_copy.png" alt="cnn.com">
 <figcaption>© cnn.com</figcaption>
 <p>Have you ever wondered what the people who stand up as soon as the plane lands do with all that extra time they saved? <br>This petition puts an end to that madness. Please support and sign!</p>
</div>
{{#if inputIncomplete}}
  {{>error }}
  {{/if}}
<div class="form-container">
<form id="signup" method="POST" action="/petition">
  <canvas id="canvas" width="200" height="40" ></canvas>
  <input type="hidden" id="signature" name="signature">
  <label class="sign-here" for="signature">Sign here</label>
  
  <input id="button" type="submit" value="Submit  ✈">
</form>
</div>
</div>
